{"tid":1031200,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VIUTV 免費播英超","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T03:13:21.000Z","uid":224375,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e35a6e2ac9ef2458d9be3eb86ddc6fbf84c990","tid":1031200,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"免費頻道ViuTV今日公佈，其99台及網絡平台，今周起將會開始免費播放英超聯，當中18/19球季會播放三場，19/20球季會播十場。該台除有專業雙語旁述，還有網上點播重溫，首場免費波將會是周六晚上11:00PM的般尼茅夫對狼隊。據大會宣傳片段，今次是相隔26年，香港再次有免費台直播英格蘭頂級聯賽。"},{"pid":"43a4cbb4bd1e51919a52655e03ed33c739bdd46b","tid":1031200,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"想睇自己家鄉球隊結果一年得10場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5782b52c7dd019d551e80b4c0aba961318a13081","tid":1031200,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"相隔26年<br />\n<br />\n即係轉英超開始已經冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265f0be1557f5762b095a2b151ff6526c0d0bec5","tid":1031200,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5782b52c7dd019d551e80b4c0aba961318a13081","tid":1031200,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"相隔26年<br />\n<br />\n即係轉英超開始已經冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"1993年 有X電視 開台&hellip;"},{"pid":"917a83c250c887fda66d7714649fce7756516fd3","tid":1031200,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265f0be1557f5762b095a2b151ff6526c0d0bec5","tid":1031200,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5782b52c7dd019d551e80b4c0aba961318a13081","tid":1031200,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"相隔26年<br />\n<br />\n即係轉英超開始已經冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-